CustomerRepresentativeMessages is a Page
    title is "Messages"

    Inbox is a Panel
        visible when (actor.agent(CustomerRepresentativeContact).IsLoggedInAndActive)
        business class is CustomerRepresentativeContactMessage
            list is PortalCustomerRepresentativeMessagesInbox
            Actions
                action is MarkAsRead
                action is MarkAsUnread
                action is MarkAsDeleted
    Trash is a Panel
        visible when (actor.agent(CustomerRepresentativeContact).IsLoggedInAndActive)
        business class is CustomerRepresentativeContactMessage
            list is PortalCustomerRepresentativeMessagesTrash
            Actions
                action is MoveToInbox
                action is DeleteForever
    Inactive is a Panel
        visible when (actor.agent(CustomerRepresentativeContact).IsLoggedInAndInactive)
        Layout
            single column
                large menu
                    paragraph
                        text of "YourAccountIsCurrentlyInactive"
                            header4
                            bold
                            italics

